---
// Sidebar card with a short note inviting reader feedback.
---

<div class="contact-card">
  <div class="contact-body">
    <p class="contact-text">
      We write because we like to hear from you. If you have thoughts on what we wrote or want to share something, we are responsive over email:
      <a href="mailto:lavaalex3@gmail.com">lavaalex3@gmail.com</a> and
      <a href="mailto:norin.lavaee@gmail.com">norin.lavaee@gmail.com</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .contact-card {
    max-width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--ctp-surface0, #313244);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    background: var(--ctp-mantle, #181825);
    transition:
      border-color 0.3s ease,
      background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .contact-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--ctp-surface1, #45475a);
  }

  .contact-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .contact-text {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--ctp-subtext1, #bac2de);
    margin: 0;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .contact-text a {
    color: var(--ctp-blue, #89b4fa);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .contact-text a:hover {
    color: var(--ctp-sky, #89dceb);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  /* Light theme overrides */
  :global([data-theme="latte"]) .contact-card {
    border-color: var(--ctp-surface0, #ccd0da);
    background: var(--ctp-mantle, #e6e9ef);
  }

  :global([data-theme="latte"]) .contact-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--ctp-surface1, #bcc0cc);
  }

  :global([data-theme="latte"]) .contact-text {
    color: var(--ctp-subtext1, #5c5f77);
  }

  :global([data-theme="latte"]) .contact-text a {
    color: var(--ctp-blue, #1e66f5);
  }

  :global([data-theme="latte"]) .contact-text a:hover {
    color: var(--ctp-sky, #04a5e5);
  }

</style>
